msgstr "Main interface has 3 entrances:"

#: .\main.lua
msgid "1. 回收物品：扫描机器周围一格（8 个相邻地格）内的物品。"
msgstr ""
"1. Recycle items: Scan items within one tile around the machine (8 adjacent "
"tiles)."

#: .\main.lua
msgid "2. 转换物品：分类，可搜索，可选具体物品并输入购买数量。"
msgstr ""
"2. Convert items: Categorized, searchable, select specific items and enter "
"purchase quantity."

#: .\main.lua
