#. ~ Description for <color_light_cyan>资源转换机</color>
#: .\modinfo.json
msgid "添加一台可建造的资源转换机。它可以回收机器周围一格的物品并把金额计入银行账号，你能购买游戏本体中的大部分物品。"
msgstr ""
"Add a buildable Resource Converter. It can recycle items within one tile "
"around the machine and credit the amount to your bank account, allowing you "
"to purchase most items from the base game."
